image 1          We've been building Magic: The Gathering Arena
in front of players for four months now (seven if you include the
NDA bit). We made some good calls and some bad calls along the
way. And you've been the ones to tell us that. Thank you for
continuing to play with us.

There is still plenty more to build, too! Which is why we're not
ready to leave Closed Beta. But, we do want to give you a way to
share our game with your friends.

Below are five MTG Arena Closed Beta access codes for you to
share. Here is how it works:

* Give a person a code. That code is single use.
* Tell that person to go to MTGArena.com.
* That person downloads the game from the website and enters
their access code.
