Break the Servers on July 20!
Extra bonus if you and your friends jump into the game on July
20! We need your help to try and break our servers. Because
breaking stuff now helps us plan for the future.

Play on Friday, July 20 between the hours of 12PM – 8PM PDT (7PM
– 3AM UTC) and get access to:

* Half-Off Draft Event. Draft Core Set 2019 for half-off (2,500
Gold or 375 Gems) with all the same rewards!
* No-Entry Constructed Event. Play in a special constructed event
with no entry fee and extra prizes.
